<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>CarZone Blog</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar px-4 py-3">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">CarZone</a>
    <div class="d-flex gap-4">
      <a href="#posts" class="nav-link">Posts</a>
      <a href="#video" class="nav-link">Video</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero text-center py-5">
    <h1 class="fw-bold">Welcome to CarZone 🏎️</h1>
    <p class="mt-2">Stories and reviews for true car lovers.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- POSTS -->
  <section id="posts" class="container py-5">
    <h3 class="section-heading mb-4">Latest Posts</h3>

    <div class="post mb-4">
      <img src="https://www.supercars.net/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1034537-2048x1328.jpg" class="post-img mb-3" alt="Ferrari"/>
      <h5>Ferrari SF90 — The Beast Unleashed</h5>
      <p>The Ferrari SF90 Stradale produces over 1000 horsepower and hits 100 km/h in just 2.5 seconds. Raw power meets cutting-edge hybrid technology.</p>
      <a href="#">Read more →</a>
    </div>
    <hr/>

    <div class="post mb-4 mt-4">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621135802920-133df287f89c?w=800" class="post-img mb-3" alt="Lamborghini"/>
      <h5>Lamborghini Huracan — Born to Race</h5>
      <p>A roaring V10 engine, jaw-dropping Italian design, and performance that takes your breath away. The Huracan is not just a car — it's an experience.</p>
      <a href="#">Read more →</a>
    </div>
    <hr/>

    <div class="post mb-4 mt-4">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?w=800" class="post-img mb-3" alt="Porsche"/>
      <h5>Porsche 911 — A Timeless Classic</h5>
      <p>Since 1963, the Porsche 911 has defined what a sports car should be. Decade after decade it evolves, yet never loses its iconic soul.</p>
      <a href="">Read more →</a>
    </div>
    <hr/>

    <div class="post mt-4">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800" class="post-img mb-3" alt="McLaren"/>
      <h5>McLaren 720S — Lightweight Champion</h5>
      <p>Built around a carbon fibre body and powered by a twin-turbo V8, the McLaren 720S is incredibly light and blindingly fast. British engineering at its finest.</p>
      <a href="#">Read more →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VIDEO -->
  <section id="video" class="container py-4 text-center">
    <h3 class="section-heading mb-4">Watch This 🎥</h3>
    <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 mx-auto" style="max-width: 680px;">
      <iframe src="https://youtu.be/QNJL6nfu__Q?si=NtzeDcNY3w9S97Bv" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section id="contact" class="container py-5" style="max-width: 500px;">
    <h3 class="section-heading mb-4">Contact Us</h3>
    <input type="text" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Your name"/>
    <input type="email" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Your email"/>
    <textarea class="form-control mb-3" rows="4" placeholder="Your message"></textarea>
    <button class="btn btn-outline-light w-100">Send Message</button>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="text-center py-3">
    <small>CarZone 2025</small>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>


style.css

body {
  background-color: #000;
  color: #ccc;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

/* NAVBAR */
.navbar {
  background-color: #000;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
}
.navbar-brand {
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-link {
  color: #666;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-link:hover { color: #fff; }

/* HERO */
.hero {
  background-color: #000;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
  padding: 80px 20px;
}
.hero h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 2.5rem; }
.hero p { color: #555; }

/* SECTION HEADING */
.section-heading { color: #fff; }

/* POSTS */
.post h5 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.post p { color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; }
.post a { color: #aaa; font-size: 0.85rem; text-decoration: none; }
.post a:hover { color: #fff; }

hr { border-color: #222; }

/* VIDEO */
iframe { border-radius: 8px; }

/* FORM */
.form-control {
  background: #111;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  color: #fff;
  border-radius: 6px;
}
.form-control:focus {
  background: #111;
  border-color: #555;
  color: #fff;
  box-shadow: none;
}
.form-control::placeholder { color: #444; }

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  border-top: 1px solid #222;
  color: #444;
}


